Require: Query x, number of samples N, LLM M or LLM integrated with other methods f M(x)
1: Initialize an empty set for samples S ← ∅
2: for i = 1 to N doGenerate sample si ← M(x) or si ← fM(x)
3: 4:Add sample to the set S ← S U {si}
5: end for
6: for each sample si in S do
7:Initialize similarity scores V (si) ← 0
8:for each sample sj in S do
9: if i ≠ j then
10:V(si) ← V (si) + sim(si, j)
11:end if
12:end for
13: end for
15: return A14: A ← arg maxsi∈s V (si)
